   <mo accent="true" class="mo">¯</mo>
  </mover>
 </math>, Figures 
 <xref rid="grl56839-fig-0002" ref-type="fig" class="xref">2</xref>a and 
 <xref rid="grl56839-fig-0002" ref-type="fig" class="xref">2</xref>b) balances well with the net surface water budget, precipitation minus evaporation ( 
