 </math>, Figure 
 <xref rid="grl56839-supitem-0001" ref-type="supplementary-material" class="xref">S4</xref>), in both the CGCMs and AGCMs, confirming that the transient eddies play a minor role over the monsoon region (Figure 
 <xref rid="grl56839-supitem-0001" ref-type="supplementary-material" class="xref">S5</xref>). Consistent with Li et al. (
 <xref rid="grl56839-bib-0028" ref-type="ref" class="xref">2015</xref>) using a slightly larger ensemble set of nine models, the total response of 
